{"tid":238024,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Origo風扇","createTime":"2017-05-10T18:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T06:09:55.000Z","uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d399aecb82381354f02416f1f4dad767272e5c67","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg722ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg722ur.jpg&h=98c09164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我睇中左依部, 話有接近3號風球既風力, 成700蚊,<br />\n想買黎擺房用, 唔知有冇巴打用過覺得點?<br />\n<br />\n另外無印果把風扇好似都唔錯, 價錢參唔多要600, Made in Japan"},{"pid":"b9210b4937f51170f1b5a073a5ecfc9cbb26ada0","tid":238024,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg722ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg722ur.jpg&h=98c09164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我睇中左依部, 話有接近3號風球既風力, 成700蚊,<br />\n想買黎擺房用, 唔知有冇巴打用過覺得點?<br />\n<br />\n另外無印果把風扇好似都唔錯, 價錢參唔多要600, Made in Japan</blockquote><br />\n3號風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要咁勁做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabaaf06b59a96da9d5486c1d7f793dddae58274","tid":238024,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"推薦巴打整個部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e65ec1044d4f0e5205312087279bb51c4857fa","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg722ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg722ur.jpg&h=98c09164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我睇中左依部, 話有接近3號風球既風力, 成700蚊,<br />\n想買黎擺房用, 唔知有冇巴打用過覺得點?<br />\n<br />\n另外無印果把風扇好似都唔錯, 價錢參唔多要600, Made in Japan</blockquote><br />\n3號風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要咁勁做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢細細部又咁好風"},{"pid":"bb3825344c2db4c66e716bff037d5dcb119ea3e1","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推薦巴打整個部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有用過？有咩評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上冇咩依部機資料，開箱文/youtube都冇人介紹，覺得有d奇怪"},{"pid":"32b172d264f4f96f55d13c8fb11b350b3149bd5f","tid":238024,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"畀個小小建議 最好搵到有鋪頭有實物可以望望難唔難拆 有啲未必前後網都可以甩晒出嚟洗 同埋如果賣點係大風要留意會唔會好嘈"},{"pid":"35e376542a37f02177cb4b1d0ab38f5001dfecc4","tid":238024,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:02:50.000Z","msg":"呢個牌子應該有放喺啲百貨公司家電部 如果搵到有display機就最好 見有啲牌子賣點係大風既風扇通常都嘈到喊"},{"pid":"10f80b995ccae230a87644542187aa427289d058","tid":238024,"uid":64768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:12:20.000Z","msg":"呢個牌子係賣貼牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係係大陸廠買個model然後貼自己牌子上去<br />\n應該有其他牌子有差唔多款<br />\n可以比較下"},{"pid":"2e454f5812d5090fbddbe3ae0ba727fcf8f04af8","tid":238024,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個牌子係賣貼牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係係大陸廠買個model然後貼自己牌子上去<br />\n應該有其他牌子有差唔多款<br />\n可以比較下</blockquote><br />\n其實好多牌子都係咁 所以如果有行開百貨公司會發現個個牌子都差唔多款"},{"pid":"498db5b8713e04033620ea765cf2b8b9ef7de055","tid":238024,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:24:08.000Z","msg":"利申 用緊<br />\n<br />\n如果開到風力4最強既話 真係好大風 不過d風係好集中 企側少少已經唔太吹到 最重要係部機會好嘈同震曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似會散噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg&h=4416d32c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f51eb0944d3a58100e8f1f5c5d8f9bf974d2885e","tid":238024,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推薦巴打整個部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有用過？有咩評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上冇咩依部機資料，開箱文/youtube都冇人介紹，覺得有d奇怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似未整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc508e7fd71f5462858c828a092f094cfe8b0610","tid":238024,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:33:47.000Z","msg":"睇你係咪一定要搖控姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪一定要滴滴骰骰+外型有設計感<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係KDK 都有坐地/坐台扇，又平又好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fa0711d21ac9e7ac6da48f421c04849dfe4a3a","tid":238024,"uid":47681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:51:05.000Z","msg":"買過呢個牌子其他款<br />\n一年就壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5400f897461f91ea2e2ef09655ce4e7fa7afa8","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 用緊<br />\n<br />\n如果開到風力4最強既話 真係好大風 不過d風係好集中 企側少少已經唔太吹到 最重要係部機會好嘈同震曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似會散噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg&h=4416d32c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉既角度大唔大<br />\n部機真係幾靚"},{"pid":"1b2848dc4e5cf925ee2d3d64cc6cdb1c8ba92030","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個牌子係賣貼牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係係大陸廠買個model然後貼自己牌子上去<br />\n應該有其他牌子有差唔多款<br />\n可以比較下</blockquote><br />\n其實好多牌子都係咁 所以如果有行開百貨公司會發現個個牌子都差唔多款</blockquote><br />\n發覺牌子好多，但款式就參唔多"},{"pid":"3b8279e1b790d9d099abd78fe4c8ff4168f93ed4","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推薦巴打整個部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有用過？有咩評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上冇咩依部機資料，開箱文/youtube都冇人介紹，覺得有d奇怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似未整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點壞法"},{"pid":"1434a6347bb146bcebe0bfe83cddf6081e411931","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你係咪一定要搖控姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係咪一定要滴滴骰骰+外型有設計感<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係KDK 都有坐地/坐台扇，又平又好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遙控有冇都冇所謂，係貪佢細部又夠風<br />\nKDK/樂聲 依d老牌子一定耐用，但就大部冇咁慳位"},{"pid":"a32f744414d72a6878ae88e8d4fdc0e5417b5431","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"push下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他牌子好介紹？傳統風扇定係對流式既好"},{"pid":"04e141652c567c84dc6042a0254449d4d051e17c","tid":238024,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>push下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他牌子好介紹？傳統風扇定係對流式既好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對流式如果間屋唔係通風就無鬼用<br />\n但通風又洗鬼用風扇咩<br />\n<br />\n熱起上黎用傳統扇吹係無得輸"},{"pid":"b4871afdfe5ca1cf5bae0524d171ba6a63ded2cc","tid":238024,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 用緊<br />\n<br />\n如果開到風力4最強既話 真係好大風 不過d風係好集中 企側少少已經唔太吹到 最重要係部機會好嘈同震曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似會散噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg&h=4416d32c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇相，把風扇嘅吹風軌個直徑好似唔大<br />\n如果風力真係好大<br />\n被風吹果個人一來會好容易被吹到髻都甩同頭都暈<br />\n二來整體環境空間只有好少空間空氣被吹動<br />\n我以前都以為傳統直吹強風左右擺動嘅風扇係最涼<br />\n不過我而家反而覺得鴻運扇，仲要唔係極強風果種，反而仲涼<br />\n個人覺得<br />\n因為鴻運扇係180度內全方位韻律式勻循吹風<br />\n咁成個空間都會得到降溫<br />\n如果把鴻運扇係極強風，反而會將整個吹風空間打散<br />\n而風力同前面塊轉輪平衡做得好（風力冇咁大）<br />\n我覺得係會令到整個吹風空間反而仲涼快<br />\n我用開 P記嗰把鴻運扇就好滿意"},{"pid":"bf01529e13fa7706cb8d71600df4cedc0a09f624","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>push下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他牌子好介紹？傳統風扇定係對流式既好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對流式如果間屋唔係通風就無鬼用<br />\n但通風又洗鬼用風扇咩<br />\n<br />\n熱起上黎用傳統扇吹係無得輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我間房仔一到夏天就係好焗空氣又唔流通，對流式應該唔啱我用"},{"pid":"370f816464ce40fbedf6308b262887802b7bbddf","tid":238024,"uid":92906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"買過佢d風扇<br />\n一年唔夠有雜聲<br />\n唔會再買"},{"pid":"a76fd2942f0b0aeaca5a97a6cbf07ea6343a9444","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申 用緊<br />\n<br />\n如果開到風力4最強既話 真係好大風 不過d風係好集中 企側少少已經唔太吹到 最重要係部機會好嘈同震曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似會散噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F032406_90a226be940269e4b1ac817c398e20bb.jpg&h=4416d32c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇相，把風扇嘅吹風軌個直徑好似唔大<br />\n如果風力真係好大<br />\n被風吹果個人一來會好容易被吹到髻都甩同頭都暈<br />\n二來整體環境空間只有好少空間空氣被吹動<br />\n我以前都以為傳統直吹強風左右擺動嘅風扇係最涼<br />\n不過我而家反而覺得鴻運扇，仲要唔係極強風果種，反而仲涼<br />\n個人覺得<br />\n因為鴻運扇係180度內全方位韻律式勻循吹風<br />\n咁成個空間都會得到降溫<br />\n如果把鴻運扇係極強風，反而會將整個吹風空間打散<br />\n而風力同前面塊轉輪平衡做得好（風力冇咁大）<br />\n我覺得係會令到整個吹風空間反而仲涼快<br />\n我用開 P記嗰把鴻運扇就好滿意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醒唔起有鴻運扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb2445083aaec96b98d715ff65a3a73d6adde41","tid":238024,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"最後都係買返樂聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}